3. Cannot find tropical inspo that works for shorter nails — everything shows long coffins
4. Unsure which tropical aesthetic matches their specific destination (Hawaii ≠ Ibiza ≠ Caribbean)
5. Worried that intricate tropical art will chip quickly during active holiday activities (swimming, sand, sun)

